pages.text:
Holmes Creek Camping is owned by locals, we too used to camp locally when given a chance. Then we came up with the great idea to open our own campground! We opened the campground September 2022, it took us roughly two years to complete the campground but we are working to make the campground better everyday! We’re very proud of the work done thus far but have plans of expanding and adding more amenities. Our family truly enjoys hearing about each families adventures and where they plan on traveling to next. Follow us on Facebook to keep up with our progress!
